<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Your Parcel Order is Confirmed!</title>
    <style>
      body { background: #f4f6fb; font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
      .container { max-width: 480px; margin: 40px auto; background: #fff; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.07); padding: 32px 28px; }
      .logo { display: block; margin: 0 auto 18px; width: 64px; height: 64px; background: #4f8cff; border-radius: 50%; color: #fff; font-size: 32px; line-height: 64px; text-align: center; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 2px; }
      h2 { color: #22223b; margin-top: 0; }
      p { color: #444; line-height: 1.6; }
      .details { background: #e0e7ff; color: #1e293b; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 500; padding: 12px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0 16px 0; }
      .cta-btn { display: inline-block; margin-top: 18px; background: #4f8cff; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; padding: 10px 28px; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; transition: background 0.2s; }
      .cta-btn:hover { background: #2563eb; }
      .footer { margin-top: 32px; color: #888; font-size: 13px; text-align: center; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="logo">S</div>
      <h2>Your Parcel Order is Confirmed!</h2>
      <p>Hello {{name}},<br>Thank you for trusting <b>SendIT</b>! Your parcel order has been received and will be sent to <b>{{recipient}}</b> at <b>{{destination}}</b>.</p>
      <div class="details">
        <b>Tracking Number:</b> {{trackingNumber}}<br>
        <b>Estimated Delivery:</b> {{estimatedDelivery}}<br>
      </div>
      <a href="https://sendit.example.com/track?tracking={{trackingNumber}}" class="cta-btn">Track Parcel</a>
      <div class="footer">&copy; {{year}} SendIT. All rights reserved.</div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html> 